==== Exercise Physiology (2-Day CPET)

    - Day 1 and Day 2 standardized exercise protocols: ramp protocol on stationary cycle ergometer
    - Primary outcome: Functional decline from Day 1 to Day 2 (reduced workload capacity)
    - Secondary: Peak oxygen consumption, ventilatory threshold, heart rate response
    - Muscle biopsy (vastus lateralis): Electron microscopy, respiratory chain enzyme activities, mtDNA copy number, ATP content

